Given the following code excerpt that defines an SAP HANA database table:
DEFINE TABLE demo_table
{
    KEY field1 : REFERENCE TO abap.cInt(3);
    KEY field2 : abap.char(1337);      @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure:'demo_table.field4'
    field3 : abap.quan(2);
    field4 : abap.unit(2);
}
Which field is defined incorrectly?
